original_title: James Last: Gold Top live – Das Beste aus der ZDF-„Starparade“
overview: James Last and his orchestra in recordings of the series “Starparade” by the German TV station ZDF. The musical television series was produced from 1968 to 1980 and was closely associated with James Last.
title: James Last: Gold Top live – Das Beste aus der ZDF-„Starparade“
